definition: Annual estimates were produced for overweight prevalence for children under 5 years of age at the 5x5 km-level for 105 low- and middle-income countries (LMICs) between 2000 and 2019.
title: Global Under-5 Overweight Prevalence Geospatial Estimates 2000-2019
citation: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation (IHME). Global Under-5 Overweight Prevalence Geospatial Estimates 2000-2019. Seattle, United States of America: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation (IHME), 2020
